|RB0The Sidhe are a race of vile demonic creatures originating from the
influential fae population of Talamh Darag. These Sidhe were infected
by a vampiric condition affecting their society on a large level. 
The now unseelie Sidhe are known for their evil acts, magical abilities
and the moth-like wings that enable them to ascend from the ground.
The magical nature of the Sidhe fae allows them to regenerate their
abilities with greater ease then any other race would be able to.
Their weak body is able to purge toxics from their bloodstream at an 
increased rate, but suffers greatly where raw physical power is concerned.

